snippet.title: Rockman X - Prelaunch Trailer
snippet.description:
In celebration of the launch of another X Collection, here is a lengthy trailer for Rockman X shown at Shoshinkai '93. 

There are many small differences in this beta compared to the final game, most notably the explosion effect and the mid-charge buster shot being red instead of the final green color. 

#MegaManX
